{"tid":647939,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[贏到英國] 英國納稅人因郵政條約漏洞 長期資助贏國Ebay零售商攻陷英國市場","createTime":"2018-04-30T09:18:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T02:43:55.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fd030552bfca6ad0a6af5bf07e078974716c067d","tid":647939,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:18:48.000Z","msg":"英國納稅人因郵政條約漏洞 長期資助契丹Ebay零售商攻陷英國市場<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://gaus.ee/2018/04/vat-royal-mail-loophole/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgaus.ee%2F2018%2F04%2Fvat-royal-mail-loophole%2F&d=2a7ilcOh5yBi5M4PnETHk6NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=b6f9a9d0\" target=\"_blank\">http://gaus.ee/2018/04/vat-royal-mail-loophole/</a><br />\n<br />\n倫敦 &ndash; 最近一個郵政條約漏洞，搞到英國要用納稅人資助契丹，可能包括香港嘅小物製造業 ，惹黎政界震驚。<br />\n<br />\n皇家郵政為鼓勵發展中國家製造業，一直以低於成本價鼓勵加蓬、哈薩克、古巴等國包裹寄入英國做銷售用途。<br />\n<br />\n契丹也是受惠國之一，英國製造商製造一支英國國旗，用皇家郵政送貨成本要1.26鎊，而契丹製造商利用郵政漏洞，加上懷疑政府協助壓價，利用低於15鎊進口貨免增值稅嘅歐盟條款，成本可以低到1.19鎊。香港一個製造商賣白板擦，可以低價到18英仙，皇家郵政仲可以免佢郵費。<br />\n<br />\n因此大量契丹商戶，係Amazon 同 Ebay 開店，大肆利用呢個漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">美國都有類似條款，但本月已經開始立法堵塞漏洞，但英國政府至今未有反應。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/d413aa84-44dd-11e8-9618-96ec7a8a2ce5?utm_source=on9.si&amp;utm_medium=gaus.ee&amp;utm_campaign=on9.si%2F1d8yY&amp;utm_content=link_click\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fd413aa84-44dd-11e8-9618-96ec7a8a2ce5%3Futm_source%3Don9.si%26utm_medium%3Dgaus.ee%26utm_campaign%3Don9.si%252F1d8yY%26utm_content%3Dlink_click&d=2a7ilcOh5yBi5M4PnETHk6NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=2216db94\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/d413aa84-44dd-11e8-9618-96ec7a8a2ce5?utm_source=on9.si&amp;utm_medium=gaus.ee&amp;utm_campaign=on9.si%2F1d8yY&amp;utm_content=link_click</a>"},{"pid":"d6e259f53eee0cf76f02017004874e4947cfd1dc","tid":647939,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:21:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n贏到英國自己投降"},{"pid":"03bdc6c4b72a8f19794a1fbefe272fb4e34cb1ef","tid":647939,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:25:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acad49b1be68e66b20dc85ad205007d7f4a9bc09","tid":647939,"uid":130105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"唚日先起國會嘈完，英國正苦每年比四萬磅（？？）去贏國扶貧。"},{"pid":"e5601335ade8742226d4fd54600029dda90c1f5a","tid":647939,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T01:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3502449efe94fef66c43cdf43c31ec9eac6cfe8","tid":647939,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acad49b1be68e66b20dc85ad205007d7f4a9bc09","tid":647939,"uid":130105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"唚日先起國會嘈完，英國正苦每年比四萬磅（？？）去贏國扶貧。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T01:37:37.000Z","msg":"贏国唔洗人扶貧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313e520250107189c5ed13b0bd2eabc5420f5bcb","tid":647939,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T03:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465290ab2f890adfeae3d68945b350f12a7bc981","tid":647939,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}